name: DigitalDashboardPluginHeatMap
description: Visualization component for the old version of the DigitalDashboard. Expects to be connected as a child to the DigitalDashboard Webble. Draws heat maps. Can do clustering of the rows and/or columns. Allows selection of rows, columns, or cells based on the value in the cell. Can generate item set data based on selected cells.
author: legacyDigitalDashboard
